StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetCi.es]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @StateCode varchar(3), @CountyCode varchar(4) = NULL ) AS
SELECT ID, Code, [Name] FROM [USMC].[vwCi.es] WHERE StateCode = @StateCode AND CountyCode = COALESCE(@CountyCode, CountyCode) AND [Name] IS NOT NULL ORDER BY [Name]
